T1  - Alterations in Local Peri-Infarct Blood Gases in Stroke Patients Undergoing Thrombectomy.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.wneu.2021.10.171
A1  - Spears, Robert Christopher
A1  - McLouth, Christopher J
A1  - Pennypacker, Keith R
A1  - Frank, Jacqueline A
A1  - Maglinger, Benton
A1  - Martha, Sarah
A1  - Trout, Amanda L
A1  - Roberts, Jill
