T1  - Association of variants in HTRA1 and NOTCH3 with MRI-defined extremes of cerebral small vessel disease in older subjects.
T3  - Comment in: Brain. 2019 Nov 1;142(11):e61 PMID: 31603204 [https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/31603204]
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1093/brain/awz024
A1  - Mishra, Aniket
A1  - Chauhan, Ganesh
