T1  - MIRACUM: Medical Informatics in Research and Care in University Medicine.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.3414/ME17-02-0025
A1  - Prokosch, Hans-Ulrich
A1  - Acker, Till
A1  - Bernarding, Johannes
A1  - Binder, Harald
A1  - Boeker, Martin
A1  - Boerries, Melanie
A1  - Daumke, Philipp
